description:
A being born from the organic spaceship that hosts the true Chojin (Overfiend). They`re the forefront of a new human race with a power that defies the current three realms (Human, Beast, Demon), with the power of imagination to turn the tide in any conflict and use mind-control to their advantage. 
They don`t have any distinct sexual organs and can manifest both while even giving birth to oneself.
name: Mizuchi
